BUG-09: Accepts Negative "Tip %"

Severity: Medium

Environment: Windows 11, Chrome Browser

Steps to Reproduce (STR):

1)Navigate to the "Expense Splitter."

2)Enter -10 for "Tip %."

3)Click "Calculate."

Expected Result: An error message like "Tip percentage cannot be negative" should be displayed.

Actual Result: The app accepts the negative value and incorrectly calculates a discounted total.

Evidence: 
 ![Screenshot showing accept negative tip](evidence\bug-09-negative-tip.png)